m_q.target_metric: Name of the player with the most goals during the period 1972-1975, 1976-1982
sub_questions: Which players have a Period that exactly matches '1972 – 1975, 1976 – 1982'?
What is the Goals¹ value for each player matching this period?
Which player has the maximum Goals¹ value among the filtered results?

format_notes: Column names contain special characters (¹, ²)
Period column contains compound date ranges with specific formatting
Goals¹ and Appearances¹ columns are stored as object dtype but represent numeric values

constraints: Goals¹ must be converted to numeric type for comparison
output_format_requirements: Return the Name of the player with maximum Goals¹
Handle case where multiple players may have the same maximum goals
